26
00:00:59,226 --> 00:01:02,361
- Ali tvoja bolest. - Moja bi te krv mogla spasiti.

27
00:01:02,496 --> 00:01:04,696
Zvona zvone.

28
00:01:04,832 --> 00:01:09,033
Gong, gong, gong!

29
00:01:09,070 --> 00:01:10,635
I rezati!

30
00:01:11,472 --> 00:01:12,749
Stao si mi na crtu. Opet.

31
00:01:12,773 --> 00:01:14,484
Ja... nisam namjeravao.

32
00:01:14,508 --> 00:01:16,175
- Kristin, čekaj. - Hej.

33
00:01:16,310 --> 00:01:18,288
Ne, ne, ne. Slušaj me ti.

34
00:01:18,312 --> 00:01:19,845
Ovo je o mojoj novoj liniji odjeće.

35
00:01:19,980 --> 00:01:21,024
Dizajneri rade ono što ja kažem.

36
00:01:21,048 --> 00:01:22,247
